{"tid":1480562,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[818] 羅文《獅子山下》，四十年前就教咗香港人「兄弟爬山」嘅真諦","createTime":"2019-08-17T10:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T16:16:55.000Z","uid":15935,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a3787baac4cefa78c062cd2a84de6789c4bc98","tid":1480562,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"《獅子山下》簡直係香港國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作曲：顧家輝<br />\n填詞：黃霑<br />\n<br />\n人生中有歡喜 難免亦常有淚<br />\n我哋大家 在獅子山下相遇上<br />\n總算是歡笑多於唏噓<br />\n<br />\n人生不免崎嶇 難以絕無掛慮<br />\n既是同舟 在獅子山下且共濟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拋棄區分求共對<br />\n<br />\n放開彼此心中矛盾 理想一起去追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼</span><br />\n<br />\n同處海角天邊 攜手踏平崎嶇<br />\n我哋大家 用艱辛努力寫下那<br />\n不朽香江名句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放開彼此心中矛盾 理想一起去追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼<br />\n<br />\n同處海角天邊 攜手踏平崎嶇<br />\n我哋大家 用艱辛努力寫下那<br />\n不朽香江名句"},{"pid":"7390b2566ea86c8cfed59119d3cdc7e696eb54be","tid":1480562,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrJrLgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrJrLgG.jpg&h=d354981c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMZbbWG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMZbbWG.jpg&h=b5e6b6ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6e61af8068bd49795ca691b5f962a2960188d34","tid":1480562,"uid":32694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"國歌其實正正形容緊一班勇武。"},{"pid":"65e598ae82c023877269a41c7b15856a9dd35e05","tid":1480562,"